        Create a walker object to traverse content graph and submits events to an event manager. Normally the event manager is a WalkerManager object that can foward events to infantium servers or infantium debugger.
        Parameters:
        in - Content Craph file
        evt_manager - object that implements WalkerEventManager interface to receive events
